body:
The following code with a delayed increment causes a segfault.

@kbieganski perhaps you could take a look? Thanks.

```
module t;
   int   ia;
   int   ib;

   initial begin
      ia = 0;
      #1 ib = ++ia;
      #1
        if (ia !== ib) $stop;

      #1 ib = ia++;
      #1
        if (ia == ib) $stop;
      #10;

      $write("*-* All Finished *-*\n");
      $finish;
   end
endmodule

```
